      <title>由于当地人受到更高利率的吸引，外国人成为土耳其股票的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/foreigners-key-to-turkish-stocks-as-locals-lured-by-higher-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于较高的存款利率可能会削弱土耳其股市对国内投资者的吸引力，外国资本流入可能是市场延续四分之一个多世纪以来最长涨势的最佳机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/foreigners-key-to-turkish-stocks-as-locals-lured-by-higher-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 05:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
