      <title>北京裁定台湾对中国商品的禁令是贸易壁垒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-determines-taiwan-s-ban-on-mainland-goods-is-trade-barrier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国认定台湾对中国进口的禁令构成贸易壁垒，这一决定是在这个自治岛屿举行关键总统选举前一个月作出的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-determines-taiwan-s-ban-on-mainland-goods-is-trade-barrier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 03:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的政策组合给投资者带来市场反弹的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-expands-cash-coffers-with-13th-consecutive-loan-injection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向经济注入创纪录数量的现金的同时，也对房地产行业重新提供了支持，在零敲碎打的做法让投资者感到沮丧之后，向投资者发出了更强有力的刺激信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-expands-cash-coffers-with-13th-consecutive-loan-injection</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 01:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
